Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么会在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.89,0:00:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.56,0:00:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  要喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.03,0:00:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真稀奇呢  贵史君竟然会帮忙运送货物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.64,0:02:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  很少见呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬语？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.39,0:02:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是学长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你笑我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那么一本正经啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水越同学什么时候搬家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.17,0:02:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季？  她说过要搬家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是下月底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:02:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉他纱季的邮箱地址了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  这种事得先征求本人同意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.53,0:03:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你表哥会不会去向纱季告白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢过学长他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别用过去式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他明明说过不喜欢比他小的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为纱季看上去很成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我就是个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要烫卷发试试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样撑不过一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕纱季啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果  如果我也变成纱季那样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季  纱季！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这突然是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么夏海会在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  这里是哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是纱季啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  我是纱季吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季  你到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:04:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是优香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我变成纱季了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你们干的好事！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季  你是被撞傻了吗  要不要去保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的表哥  贵史君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海你以前也和他一起玩过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.81,0:05:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  纱季你有表哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水越同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海你去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水越同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里巧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说你要搬家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:05:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要去东京吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:05:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就去  抱歉  下次再说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能给你发邮件吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系  不就是约一次会嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约… 你还有这种企图啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得变成纱季了  让我也做一次白日梦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和学长一起出门的话优香不也可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要装成纱季的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  装样子也行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.93,0:07:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海也有吧  只要在一起就会觉得满足的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说Four Season的秋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(407,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Akira
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想象一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海成为了Four Season的一员  就当做是冬好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(470,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Fuyumi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个短暂的白日梦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么做才能变回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概实现我的愿望就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会是绝对不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香没什么体力才会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的身体好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨她进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了防止你逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.02,0:08:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能够恢复原样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够改变已经许下的愿望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变回来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.19,0:08:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有好好许愿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许过了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次  一二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我更加真诚点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.65,0:08:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.03,0:08:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是变不回来了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…被自己发火了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想对自己发火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去真有意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.97,0:09:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说的事不关己的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  优香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了要变回来  其它什么事都不要去想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的表情变得和纱季一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二  希望能恢复原样  优香！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能恢复原样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回不来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是凛子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:09:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  夏海  这可是凛子的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让你来帮点忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉小凛好像有点不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  凛子非常有精神  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.72,0:10:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能暴露神石的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有去约会了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊  凛子也只能回夏海家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海一直要为大树准备午饭的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\an8}（明天能见面吗？）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会做点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉拌青菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.66,0:10:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉拌青菜？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水族馆？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  听说海豚奈绪子在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过了中午看完企鹅之后去吃午饭是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后去看海狮表演  完了再去看海豚表演
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就亲亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.93,0:11:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不亲亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没什么人的昏暗的水族馆里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围一个人也没有  于是在那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.82,0:11:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  就因为凛说了奇怪的话  我开始紧张起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.79,0:11:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能装得像纱季一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.46,0:11:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被发现是我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也一直用这个表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛不阻止我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望我阻止你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺负人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香的愿望就是我的愿望  我支持你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛  最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了  这是零花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吗  之前还总是求着要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.40,0:12:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…太好了太好了  我要我要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.16,0:12:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香还真是一点都没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要成为Four Season一样的偶像哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么首先就要练习唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季太严格了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想成为偶像的话这是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来邮件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家早  给你们添麻烦了  真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望马上就能实现了  然后肯定能变回原样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  能再等一等的话我会很高兴  优香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.74,0:13:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\an8}（早上好）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海  你打算睡到什么时候  快起来  夏海  夏海！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}等等  这样就像是在说我贪睡似的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.72,0:14:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找姐姐有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大树  你出去玩了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能去叫你姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  你朋友来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.09,0:14:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大树  优香…不对  你知道纱季去哪里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才看到她和男人走在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.85,0:14:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险的  坐下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用  没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚开走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到水族馆要20分钟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那么拼命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最不能跑的就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点阻止优香的话  不知道她会做出什么来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离演出还有点时间  进里面去慢慢逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有暑假补习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天没关系…不如说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.77,0:15:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.07,0:16:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  兴奋过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.76,0:16:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是纱季  我是纱季
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.97,0:16:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香也经常做那个动作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:16:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  比起那个你衣服没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉气氛很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不回去  她要是想做什么奇怪的事我们得马上去阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的事是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是…接吻什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吗  第一次约会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道  但是说不准吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们追
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵史就在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不可思议的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前明明也经常一起玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天谢谢你了  我玩得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果  如果就这样一切都停止下来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵史君？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦  就直接叫我名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵史君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  那你就叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也…也直接叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.58,0:19:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会哭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季  同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始我就知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.82,0:19:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵史君喜欢的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在贵史君眼中的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.84,0:20:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香？  谁是优香？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打断了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明说过要支持你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很想和他亲亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.35,0:20:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  已经没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎变回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.22,0:21:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥  我们要关门了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水越同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了优香  我才有了这段美好的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.69,0:21:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了优香？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重  吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了  竟然连个表情符都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.25,0:21:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在拒绝的邮件里怎么能加上心之类的表情符
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这辈子都没可能成为纱季的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这当然了  优香就是优香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.64,0:21:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因为  优香就是优香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.60,0:22:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.70,0:22:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.41,0:22:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么  告诉我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我们来比谁先跑到便利店
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.06,0:22:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁输了请客喝果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.15,0:22:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.78,0:22:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  完全跑不动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香没体力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真罗嗦  你们等等我
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.50,0:24:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  优香竟然用我的身体去约会
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.24,0:24:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再追究了  都已经过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.37,0:24:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要追究  一定要报复她
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.17,0:24:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要报复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.49,0:24:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是挨打不还手的纱季大人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.86,0:24:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香  你要忍住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.60,0:24:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集  夏色奇迹  第五话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.35,0:24:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热感冒和鲸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.04,0:24:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季  就算是要报复  但你让她得感冒真的是做得太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.42,0:24:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  我还什么都没做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
